headline: Stifel Raises its Price Target on FedEx Corporation (FDX) to $412 and Maintains a Buy Rating
summary: FedEx Corporation (NYSE:FDX) is among the 11 Best All-Time High Stocks to Buy According to Wall Street. On February 13, 2026, Stifel analyst J. Bruce Chan raised the price target on FedEx Corporation (NYSE:FDX) to $412 from $328 and maintained a Buy rating after the company hosted an Investor Day outlining its mid-term strategic roadmap […]
